Setup:
 * gem install rails -v 2.2.2 or rake rails:freeze:edge TAG=rel_2_2_2
 * install databse adapter if necessary (gem install sqlite3-ruby or mysql)
 * install ImageMagick
 * git clone wefootball.git
 * create and edit config/database.yml (a template in config/database.yml.template)
 * rake gems:build 

Run Tests:
 * rake db:migrate RAILS_ENV=test
 * rake test RAILS_ENV=test
